dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T16:09:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742dbb4edf3c30a4ddfe727b178a50fb61d5463c","tid":1920692,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T16:12:52.000Z","msg":"搭巴士時手袋背囊永遠擺係大脾上<br />\n冇可能就咁放係隔離位<br />\n除咗公德心外<br />\n更加唔使擔心大頭蝦漏低<br />\n唉...點都好希望佢搵得番"},{"pid":"dd4b6b3a9bdf075dca328021ffb018da29d43edc","tid":1920692,"uid":271365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"742dbb4edf3c30a4ddfe727b178a50fb61d5463c","tid":1920692,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T16:12:52.000Z","msg":"搭巴士時手袋背囊永遠擺係大脾上<br />\n冇可能就咁放係隔離位<br />\n除咗公德心外<br />\n更加唔使擔心大頭蝦漏低<br />\n唉...點都好希望佢搵得番"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T16:18:16.000Z","msg":"九巴個PO入面有提到有小朋友嘅「葬紙」<br />\n可能事主仲係未平復到心情<br />\n心神彷忽咪可能漏低個袋囉"},{"pid":"e044d687323748e00c4fd382e8b3bbfdc9b43cf0","tid":1920692,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T16:25:18.000Z","msg":"希望巴打搵到"},{"pid":"4cb54cb729509ac10c8e9160641c8e019662bc2a","tid":1920692,"uid":149779,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:19:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cffb75fc91ad8edc534cfc93f5b192f160893dcd","tid":1920692,"uid":327209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:41:23.000Z","msg":"巴打搵到未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051907cbbb17546f4a594ecafc9bcc1bfc08a1e5","tid":1920692,"uid":120807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:47:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ddae7189ad99e44750001651388015d48b3f394","tid":1920692,"uid":299164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:16:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2591775/?r=mcsdfb&amp;fbclid=IwAR0yxr7G2fsdjKg-hf8VA2xl2fEcm_FbPtDQgsWHzcLxXjF5HIclwmvclrk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2591775%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb%26fbclid%3DIwAR0yxr7G2fsdjKg-hf8VA2xl2fEcm_FbPtDQgsWHzcLxXjF5HIclwmvclrk&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0studFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=158c17f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2591775/?r=mcsdfb&amp;fbclid=IwAR0yxr7G2fsdjKg-hf8VA2xl2fEcm_FbPtDQgsWHzcLxXjF5HIclwmvclrk</a><br />\n早前爸爸表示一直未找回，有感可能是天意叫他放下，不要牽掛亡兒。今日（16日）有好消息，他在Telegram表示找回，是自己一直記錯，對大家表示抱歉及感激。<br />\n<br />\n搵返啦，原來唔係留咗係車，係留咗喺餐廳。對唔住麻煩咗大家咁耐。<br />\n<br />\n【愛兒遺物】港爸乘九巴遺亡兒出世紙及葬紙 九巴出帖與連登巴打一同助尋失物<br />\n<br />\n爸爸表示完全忘記背囊留在餐廳，一直記錯留在巴士上，他表示是餐廳員工在銀包內搵到學生證，今日學校打給他才知道。<br />\n<br />\n此外爸爸多謝大家關心，始終家人離世，需要時間平靜，希望事件告一段落。事件發生5日後终於失而復得，網民替他感到安慰，希望他跟家人好好平復心情。"},{"pid":"a90d82f25758e0a6fbbc156c785966515451023d","tid":1920692,"uid":86449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:56:23.000Z","msg":"Good"},{"pid":"2a99dfafa9beac3bbd699260a485f577ba6664a5","tid":1920692,"uid":1515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ddae7189ad99e44750001651388015d48b3f394","tid":1920692,"uid":299164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:16:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2591775/?r=mcsdfb&amp;fbclid=IwAR0yxr7G2fsdjKg-hf8VA2xl2fEcm_FbPtDQgsWHzcLxXjF5HIclwmvclrk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2591775%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb%26fbclid%3DIwAR0yxr7G2fsdjKg-hf8VA2xl2fEcm_FbPtDQgsWHzcLxXjF5HIclwmvclrk&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0studFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=158c17f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2591775/?r=mcsdfb&amp;fbclid=IwAR0yxr7G2fsdjKg-hf8VA2xl2fEcm_FbPtDQgsWHzcLxXjF5HIclwmvclrk</a><br />\n早前爸爸表示一直未找回，有感可能是天意叫他放下，不要牽掛亡兒。今日（16日）有好消息，他在Telegram表示找回，是自己一直記錯，對大家表示抱歉及感激。<br />\n<br />\n搵返啦，原來唔係留咗係車，係留咗喺餐廳。對唔住麻煩咗大家咁耐。<br />\n<br />\n【愛兒遺物】港爸乘九巴遺亡兒出世紙及葬紙 九巴出帖與連登巴打一同助尋失物<br />\n<br />\n爸爸表示完全忘記背囊留在餐廳，一直記錯留在巴士上，他表示是餐廳員工在銀包內搵到學生證，今日學校打給他才知道。<br />\n<br />\n此外爸爸多謝大家關心，始終家人離世，需要時間平靜，希望事件告一段落。事件發生5日後终於失而復得，網民替他感到安慰，希望他跟家人好好平復心情。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:13:05.000Z","msg":"搵得返就好<br />\n希望巴打可以好好生活落去"}]}